2026-05-17T00:18:58.8670223Z 13    <!--
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8670880Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8671819Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
