2026-05-17T00:18:58.8680524Z 22    <!--
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8681110Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8681851Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8682527Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8683374Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8684187Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8685025Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8685847Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8686741Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8687562Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8688336Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8688947Z 33    -->
2026-05-17T00:18:58.8689573Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
