2026-05-17T00:18:58.9365733Z 246            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-17T00:18:58.9366601Z 247            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-17T00:18:58.9367474Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-17T00:18:58.9368340Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-17T00:18:58.9369091Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-17T00:18:58.9400282Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-17T00:18:58.9401295Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-17T00:18:58.9402192Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-17T00:18:58.9403059Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-17T00:18:58.9403805Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
