2026-05-17T00:18:59.2986995Z 12    <!--
2026-05-17T00:18:59.2987373Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-17T00:18:59.2987722Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-17T00:18:59.2988434Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-17T00:18:59.2988806Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-17T00:18:59.2989225Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-17T00:18:59.2989458Z 18        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-17T00:18:59.2989622Z 19    -->
2026-05-17T00:18:59.2990327Z 20    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
